@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pftjsa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.78 * (wp.cos(tmp + 0.24) / 0.62))
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v0 + 0.47)) - wp.abs((v2 + 0.98 / tmp + 0.10)))
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = ((0.32 / v1) - ((v0 + 0.11 / v1 + 0.89) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.75)))
    v1 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.48 * tmp + 0.42)) / v1)
    tmp = (v0 / wp.exp(tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
